## 2. Objective
The objective of this report is to evaluate the quality of the sales dataset before it is used for analytics and dashboard development. This ensures that insights generated are accurate, reliable, and business-read.

---

## 3. Data Souces
Souces                              Description
Sales Data                          Transaction -level sales records
Product Data                        Product master information
Customer Data                       Customer demographics and segmentation
Data Table                          Calender reference data

