## 11. Recommendations
  Implement validation rules at data entry level
  Create centralized data governance system
  Use automated ETL pipelines for consistency
  Maintain standard reference tables (region, product, etc.)
  Schedule periodic data quality audits

---

## 12. Conclusion

The dataset is usable for business intelligence purposes after cleaning, but requires standardization improvements to achieve enterprise-grade data reliability.

